# --- Beads / Dolt files (added by bd init) ---
# --- BMAD resolved config: installer-generated, bakes in personal identity ---
# --- BMAD working scratch: canonical outputs are promoted to docs/ ---
# --- Build output (grows with the app) ---
# --- Go ---
# --- Node / frontend ---
# --- OS / editor noise ---
# --- Personal / per-contributor (never shared) ---
# --- Wails ---
# Source of truth is the committed *.toml. Regenerate via the BMAD installer.
frontend/dist/*
# .gitkeep is the stable anchor for //go:embed all:frontend/dist so `go build
# ./...` compiles on a clean checkout without a frontend build. The real build
# output (index.html + hashed assets) is regenerated by `wails build` and stays
# ignored, so it never churns. Negation must follow the ignore — last match wins.
!frontend/dist/.gitkeep
frontend/node_modules/
nocx
node_modules/
Thumbs.db
vendor/

